name: Suzuki Burgman Street 125
description: The motor of the Suzuki Burgman Street 125 is compliant with BS6 emission norms. Also, the engine features fuel injection, which ensures smoother power delivery. Also, you get a better fuel efficiency when compared to scooters with carbureted fuel delivery system. The engine can produce 8.7 BHP with 10 Nm of torque.

name: Suzuki Access 125
description: Suzuki Access 125 is a scooter available at a starting price of Rs. 77,250 in India. It is available in 6 variants and 14 colours with top variant price starting from Rs. 86,705. The Suzuki Access 125 is powered by 124cc BS6 engine which develops a power of 8.6 bhp and a torque of 10 Nm.

name: Suzuki V-Strom SX
description: The Suzuki V-Strom SX features a fully digital instrument cluster with turn-by-turn navigation and Bluetooth connectivity, and displays info such as call notifications, message alerts, speed exceeding warning, phone battery level display and ETA. Additionally, it features a USB charging socket and Suzuki Easy start system.

name: Suzuki Intruder
description: The bike is available in 7 variants with 3 colour options. The 154.9 cc engine of Intruder is mated with 5 gears, producing maximum power of 13.41,14.59,14.60 bhp @ 8000 rpm and a maximum torque of 14.00 Nm @ 6000 rpm.
